  		<div class="col-xs-6">
  			<p class="lead">Create and Share Events</p>
  			<p>Whether it's an art workshop, a jazz show, a coding class, or a soccer game - Venü helps connect you to people with spaces that can enable you to make your ideas happen.</p>
  		</div>
  		<div class="col-xs-6">
  			<p class="lead">Share Your Unused Spaces</p>
  			<p>Many spaces are not used at capacity - maybe you have an empty garage, or a guest room with no guests, or your restaurant's venue isn't always booked. Venü helps connect you with people with ideas for how to convert your empty spaces into a venue for all kinds of incredible events.</p>
  		</div>
  		
  	</div><!-- /row -->

	<div class="row mt centered ">
		<div class="col-xs-4 col-xs-offset-4" id="discover-events">
			<h3>Popular Events</h3>
			<hr>
		</div>
	</div><!-- /row -->

	<div class="row mt">
		<% @events.last(5).each do |event| %>
			<div class="col-xs-4 col-xs-4 col-xs-12 desc">
				<%= link_to image_tag(event.avatar(:medium), class: "home-images"), event_path(event), class: "b-link-fade b-animate-go" %>

				</a>
				<p><%= link_to event.name, event_path(event) %> <b><p class="lead"><%=event.user.email %></b></p></p>
				<p class="lead"><%= truncate(event.description, length: 150, separator: ' ') %></p>
				<hr-d>
			</div><!-- col-xs-4 -->
		<% end %>

		<div class="col-xs-4 col-xs-4 col-xs-12 desc">
			<a class="b-link-fade b-animate-go" href="/events/new"><img src="/img/portfolio/addevent.jpg" alt="" class="home-images">
				<div class="b-wrapper">
			  	<h4 class="b-from-left b-animate b-delay03">Add Your Own Event</h4>
			  	<p class="b-from-right b-animate b-delay03">Find a space for your passions.</p>
				</div>
			</a>
			<p>Create an event!</p>
			<p class="lead">Have an idea for an awesome workshop, class, comedy show, concert, or more? Or do you simply need a small studio place every week to work on some paintings? Venü will help you find the best spaces for your needs. </p>
			<hr-d>
		</div><!-- col-xs-4 -->
	</div><!-- /row -->
</div><!-- /container -->

